premise_source_doc_sentence: He also authored the CliffsNotes for Ayn Rand 's Atlas Shrugged , The Fountainhead , and Anthem , and has contributed essays to volumes such as Essays on Ayn Rand 's Anthem and Essays on Ayn Rand 's We the Living .
He is curator of the Ayn Rand Archives at the Ayn Rand Institute .
He is affiliated with the Ayn Rand Institute and the Ayn Rand advocacy organization , New York Heroes Society , and is known for his public defense of Objectivism and laissez-faire capitalism .
In 2004 , he published an illustrated biography of Ayn Rand 's life titled Ayn Rand .
The Journal of Ayn Rand Studies is an academic journal devoted to the study of the philosophy of Ayn Rand .
